reviewText: I did not get what I ordered. Everything was labeled correctly from the Case artwork to the disk label. What is on the disk in "The Van Halen story, the early years". I wanted the David Lee Roth DVD. Beware of what you get.

EXCELLENT VIDEO DOCUMENTRY. IT COULD HAVE BEEN MORE INDEPTH ABOUT DAVE. I LOVE IT. THERE IS A LOT OF THINGS I DID NOT KNOW. VERY INTERESTING. THANKS FOR THE EXCELLENT SERVICE AND SPEEDY DELIVERY. THANKS AGAIN ROYCE
